import React from "react" export default function About(){ return (

Who we are

RoboTO is a coalition of engineering students from Politecnico di Torino, passionate about robotics, with the goal of building advanced robots in a challenging and immersive context in order to join the RoboMaster competitions

What we do

As a team we develop a diverse fleet of robots to participate in team battles. This helps to combine our book knowledge with practice in this field, encouraging us to build the most advanced and intelligent robots

Core members

  • Corrado De Vita
  • Francesco Guarino
  • Francesco Paoli Leonardi
  • Luca Mannini
  • Maohong Jiang
  • Marco Molino
  • Vittorio Mayellaro
